{"id":148433,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/简讯：台上校被指中国间谍判无期/","date":"2011-04-28T20:00:23Z","modified":"2011-04-28T20:00:23Z","title":"简讯：台上校被指中国间谍判无期","content":"<div>\n<p>台湾国防部说，高等军事法院判处被指为中国大陆从事间谍活动的军情局上校罗奇正无期徒刑。</p>\n<p>法院合议庭称，罗奇正在任职期间，为中共从事间谍活动、收受中共贿赂，以及利用中共提供的情资诈取工作奖金，已构成为敌方从事间谍活动等三项罪行。</p>\n<p>法院认为，罗奇正的行为已触犯多项法例，合并执行判处无期徒刑。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2011/04/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Ov1n80fXZarIuhitmsC96OYkHjY/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Ov1n80fXZarIuhitmsC96OYkHjY/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Ov1n80fXZarIuhitmsC96OYkHjY/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Ov1n80fXZarIuhitmsC96OYkHjY/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/bLNG1optRDA\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[25872]}